'[Verse 1]\n[G]Lord I lift Your name on [C]high\n[G]Lord I love to sing Your [C]praises\n[G]I''m so glad You''re in my [D]life\n[G]I''m so glad You came to [D]save us\n\n[Chorus]\n[G]You came from heaven to earth to [C]show the way\n[G]From the earth to the cross my [D]debt to pay\n[Em]From the cross to the grave from the [C]grave to the sky\n[G]Lord I lift Your name on [D]high [G]',
'G', 0, 130, '4/4', 'Verse1, Chorus', 1, TRUE),

(40, 'Agnus Dei', 'Michael W. Smith', 'Michael W. Smith', 'english',
