'[Verse 1]\n[D]I need You to soften my [A]heart\nTo break me a[Bm]part\n[D]I need You to open my [A]eyes\nTo see that You''re shaping my [G]life\n[D]All I am I sur[A]render [G]\n\n[Chorus]\n[Bm]Give me faith to [G]trust what You say\n[D]That You''re good and Your [A]love is great\n[Bm]I''m broken inside [G]I give You my [D]life [A]\n\n[Bridge]\n[G]I may be weak but Your [D]Spirit''s strong in me\n[G]My flesh may fail my [A]God You never will [D]',
'D', 0, 68, '4/4', 'Verse1, Chorus, Bridge, Chorus', 1, TRUE),

